      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NOAH BONKERS (1) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 2.75 lengths at this track in a handy 19.83 beating Snidely Whiplash. Great chance again. RED ROCK RATTLER (7) was big odds last time but gave a huge sight after a fast early split, grabbed late but holding on to a placing when a 4 length second (19.79) over 340m at this track. Can measure up. MY MACHINE (4) goes very well at this journey here having never missed the frame including two wins and two placings. Missed the frame latest (22.57) when sixth over 388m at Gosford in a NG. Looks a key chance on best figures. SWEET BEVELY ANN (2) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.",
